Class ActionResult<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.bfox1.utils.ActionResult<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Any Object you want to be carried upon returning an Action Result.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IActionResult<T>
    public class ActionResult<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IActionResult<T>
    A Simple Result class to be used when a Action was Successful or not. Examples of ActionResults use, check out Command.execute(IEvent, LinkedList)
